                            <comment id="12803712" author="drwoods" created="Fri, 22 Jan 2010 14:42:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The plan was to create a openjpa-osgi artifact that includes the OSGi metadata and RFC 143 code, so we have a competitive offering to Eclipselink....  I&apos;ll try to get the openjpa artifact updated today before I cut the Beta branch, but long-term, we need a better solution than creating a jar that is not OSGi complete.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
